tvSpecials.title: Taurus Season Ep4 P4 - Earth Signs - Tarotscopes with Adam
tvSpecials.shortDescription:
Earth Signs (Taurus, Virgo, Capricorn) |

Four of Swords, King of Swords...reversed! There's a liar on hand, not healed, marriage falling apart, player energy, no empathy, watch out! There's also a Leap of Faith...find out more!

tvSpecials.title: Taurus Season Ep4 P3 - Air Signs - Tarotscopes with Adam
tvSpecials.shortDescription: Air Signs (Gemini, Libra, Aquarius) - Still dealing with the shakeup from March! Prince of Cups, the Hangman? It's not working out, bad choices, judgement, not moving forward. BUT, there's nurturing, loving, dig in, let's see what's up.

tvSpecials.title: Taurus Season Ep4 P2 - Water Signs - Tarotscopes with Adam
tvSpecials.shortDescription:

tvSpecials.shortDescription: S2 E11 Anthony Vanity - The Rebel Buzz
tvSpecials.longDescription:
@AnthonyVanity is a multi talented artist from Brazil who moved to New York City at the young age of 17 to pursue a career in the creative field. Anthony has worked as an art director for HX Magazine, held the head designer role at playgirl and most importantly, he was the creator of internet drama culture during MySpace/Stickam days. As an early internet days “influencer”, Anthony had a short lived music career with bops including “Makeup Whore” and “My Vanity isn’t fair”, you can find the 10 year anniversary album on Spotify. 

Nowadays, Anthony resides in Los Angeles, CA where he owns and operates an art studio in which he photographs influencers and entertainers as well as creates music videos for trending and upcoming musicians. Anthony will soon be starting his online series “The Vanity Show” and is releasing his coffee table book of his photography work as well as limited prints of a few selected pieces.

tvSpecials.shortDescription: We catch up with Eddie Danger, everything from his sex life, his fitness, his he is handling his porn career in COVID times. He talks about his sobriety and gives advice for anyone going through the same thing.

tvSpecials.title: What's Poppin - Who Invited Her Ep. 167

tvSpecials.title: Get Sprung - Who Invited Her Ep. 166

tvSpecials.title: Mates' Rates with Ros - Who Invited Her Ep. 165
tvSpecials.shortDescription: Ros Gelati (from our "Who Wanna Ayahuasca?" episodes) joins us this week!  She hosts a new podcast, "Mates' Rates" where she and her fellow-Aussie travel partner discuss their experience within the industry to help you save, learn & laugh.

tvSpecials.title: Hunter Harden - Who Invited Her Ep. 164
tvSpecials.shortDescription: Model, Event Host, Designer, and host of "The Real Housebears" podcast, Hunter Harden, joins the gang this week!

tvSpecials.title: Life's a Drag - Who Invited Her Ep. 163
tvSpecials.shortDescription: It's all about the DRAG this week. The Gang gets in to all of the local San Diego drag with Miss MariamT.  We talk Drag Race and how this season s never going to end. Drag Race UK  and how whinny those queens are getting across the pond.

tvSpecials.title: Worst of the Worst - Who Invited Her Ep. 162
tvSpecials.shortDescription: Worst of the Worst! This week Brynne from the Filmspringa podcast co-host the show with us. we talk worst sex story, drug stories, worst type of people, worst movies and songs of all time. Did we really need that Drag Race Episode this week?

tvSpecials.title: Mask 4 Mask - Who Invited Her Ep. 161
tvSpecials.shortDescription: We talk all about Britney. We cover RuPauls Drag Race US and UK and boy is there a lot to talk about. What this new hair trend on TikTok? We talk about new fears that this pandemic and lock s-down have caused.

tvSpecials.title: Heather Lundstedt and Stuart Matthew Price - Who Invited Her Ep. 160
tvSpecials.shortDescription: We welcome all the way from across the pond. Heather Lundstedt and Stuart Matthew Price.  If you're a musical theater junky then you're going to love this episode. Special co-host Jennie  talk all thing musical theater with Heather and Stuart

tvSpecials.title: Having Gay Sex with Ashley Gavin! - Who Invited Her Ep. 159
tvSpecials.shortDescription: Comedian and writer Ashley Gavin! Ashley is not only known for her stand-up, where she deep dives into her experiences as a gay woman and feminist, she also hosts the podcast “We’re Having Gay Sex,” a gritty show that details her queer encounters.

tvSpecials.title: Oreo, She Didn't - Who Invited Her Ep. 158
tvSpecials.shortDescription: Lady Gaga Oreos. Crumbs up, or Crumbs down? We also want to know what you think about straight actors playing LGBTQ roles. Have you seen Wanda Vision? We play a round of WTF topic roulette. We remember Cicely Tyson and Cloris Leachman

tvSpecials.title: Jewel Tones - Who Invited Her Ep. 157
tvSpecials.shortDescription: The gang re-caps the inauguration, all the fashion, the performances and what this means for our country.  What did you all thing of this weeks episode of RuPauls Drag Race? Was it a snore or an eye opener? It's someones birthday and damn he is old.

tvSpecials.title: Big Toe with Ketchup - Who Invited Her Ep. 156
tvSpecials.shortDescription: We all know the sh*t show happening in DC this week, so what else is happening out there?  The gang chats about Armie Hammer's dark text message, We also get into Tony's new obsession with Oculus Quest 2 and our best purchases made this year.

tvSpecials.title: Hen House - Who Invited Her Ep. 155
tvSpecials.shortDescription: This week Tony & Mariam T. are excited to welcome from one of the last ladies' bars in America "Gossip Grill",  Moe & Dawn! We talk about their Hen House Happy Hour, Lesbian Bar Project and all thing Gossip Grill.

tvSpecials.title: Hello 2021 - Who Invited Her podcast Ep. 154
tvSpecials.shortDescription: It's 2021 and we are ready for a fresh start! Fingers and legs crossed things will be getting better this year. This week we talk about some of our drunken stories from days we miss. We also do a RuView of RuPaul's Drag Race Season 13 premier.

tvSpecials.title: Goodbye 2020  - Who Invited Her
tvSpecials.shortDescription: We are finally saying "Peace Out" to 2020! The amazing Nina Bel Vande joins us this week as co-host!  We find out what she has been up to since we last saw her. We also have Robbie tell us what has been going on in space this past week.

tvSpecials.title: Mary, Chris My Ass - Who Invited Her?  Ep 152
tvSpecials.shortDescription: The gang is here to spread a little holiday cheer! We play  our holiday version on " Get the F*** Out" . What happened to the show last week. We talk about first impressions of Rupaul's Drag Race Season 13 Meet the Queens. Did you all see "Prom"?

tvSpecials.title: They're Back! - Who Invited Her? Ep 151
tvSpecials.shortDescription: We are back from break with Season 4!  The gang catches up on what they have been up to during our break.  We test Rob's knowledge of pop culture with a new segment called "Robbie Don't Know!"

tvSpecials.title: Murder's a Drag with Aura Van Dank  - Who Invited Her? Ep 147
tvSpecials.shortDescription: It's a murders episode with our guest Aura Van Dank host of the Murder's a Drag podcast. The gang talk some famous San Diego murders. Why people are obsessed with true crime, murders, cold case,  podcast and TV shows?  What are your favorite movies?

tvSpecials.title: Tarot with Luis - Who Invited Her? Ep 146
tvSpecials.shortDescription: The gang chats with tarot card reader, Luis.  What does he see in the T leaves for each of us?  What will our upcoming season 4 bring in our future?

tvSpecials.title: Get Game - Who Invited Her? Ep 144
tvSpecials.shortDescription: We play a round of Guess the Game Show Theme Song, we talk about our favorite games, we play a trivia game based on Who Invited Her?  How many can you get right? We even talk about some spooky games you can play.
tvSpecials.longDescription: This week it's a whole episode about games!  We play a round of Guess the Game Show Theme Song, we talk about our favorite games, we play a trivia game based on Who Invited Her?  How many can you get right? We even talk about some spooky games you can play. And we have to cover the big news of the week, Chris Evans' D***!

tvSpecials.title: Obsession - Who Invited Her? Ep 143
tvSpecials.shortDescription: This week we talk all about obsession!  What are we obsessing over, what are some things the world is obsessed with right now? We get into it all.

tvSpecials.title: Dungeons & Drag Queens - Who Invited Her? Ep 142
tvSpecials.shortDescription: Lex and Sadie from Toronto!  Together for nearly two years, recently married, and are both transgender women. Lex (they/them) is in the Sisters of Perpetual Indulgence and a  sex worker. Sadie (she/her) is a drag queen and an Assistant Professor

tvSpecials.title: Sun's Out, Buns Out! - Who Invited Her? Ep 140
tvSpecials.shortDescription: It's hot as a jockstrap this week and the gang is staying cool while talking about everything HOT!  What's your favorite summertime food, movies, traditions? We get into some hot, hot, hot topics (no, it's not The View).
